**Table of Contents**

* [Installation](#installation)

## Installation

spfy is distributed on [PyPI](https://pypi.org) as a universal
wheel and is available on Linux/macOS and Windows and supports
Python 3.6+ and PyPy.

```bash
$ pip install spfy
```
